<section id="validation">
    <title>validation</title>
    <para>Parent container for a list of rules and constraints to apply to the target text of the enclosing element.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Contains:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
        <member>- One or more <olink targetdoc="../../elements/validation/rule.xml" targetptr="rule"><code>&lt;rule></code></olink> elements.</member>
    </simplelist>
  
    <para><emphasis>Attributes:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
        <member>- attributes from other namespaces, <glossterm>optional</glossterm></member>
    </simplelist>
    
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Processing Requirements</title>

     <listitem>
      <para>When the <olink targetdoc="../../elements/validation/validation.xml" targetptr="validation"><code>&lt;validation></code></olink> element occurs at the 
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"><code>&lt;file></code></olink> level, rules <glossterm>must</glossterm> be applied to all 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/target.xml" targetptr="target"><code>&lt;target></code></olink> elements within the scope of that  
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"><code>&lt;file></code></olink> element, except where overrides are specified at the 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group"><code>&lt;group></code></olink> or 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> level.</para>
    </listitem>
    
    <listitem>
      <para>When <olink targetdoc="../../elements/validation/validation.xml" targetptr="validation"><code>&lt;validation></code></olink> occurs at the 
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group"><code>&lt;group></code></olink> level, rules <glossterm>must</glossterm> be applied to all 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/target.xml" targetptr="target"><code>&lt;target></code></olink> elements within the scope of that 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group"><code>&lt;group></code></olink>, except where overrides are specified in a nested 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group"><code>&lt;group></code></olink> element, or at the 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> level.</para>
    </listitem>
    
    <listitem>
      <para>When <olink targetdoc="../../elements/validation/validation.xml" targetptr="validation"><code>&lt;validation></code></olink> occurs at the 
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> level, rules <glossterm>must</glossterm> be applied to all 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/target.xml" targetptr="target"><code>&lt;target></code></olink> elements within the scope of that 
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>&lt;unit></code></olink>.</para>
    </listitem>
   
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
